# Commit the small StatsVault coordination files used by Codex, but keep
# bulky local caches, PDFs, query caches, and contribution artifacts ignored.
.StatsVault/*
!.StatsVault/
!.StatsVault/README.md
!.StatsVault/AGENT_INSTRUCTIONS.md
!.StatsVault/AGENTS.additions.md
!.StatsVault/project-memory.md
!.StatsVault/key-papers.md
!.StatsVault/ACTION_REQUIRED.md
!.StatsVault/references.bib
!.StatsVault/research-log.md
!.StatsVault/manifest.json
!.StatsVault/pending-markers.json
!.StatsVault/provenance.jsonl
!.StatsVault/tex/
!.StatsVault/tex/statsvault-macros.tex
!.StatsVault/notes/
!.StatsVault/notes/*.md

CLAUDE.md
